Class SeqDrift1ChangeDetector

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, ChangeDetector, MOAObject, OptionHandler

    public class SeqDrift1ChangeDetector
extends AbstractChangeDetector
    SeqDrift1ChangeDetector.java. This extends Abstract Change Detector as required by MOA. Sakthithasan, S., Pears, R., & Koh, Y. (2013). One Pass Concept Change Detection for Data Streams. In J. Pei, V. Tseng, L. Cao, H. Motoda, & G. Xu (Eds.), Advances in Knowledge Discovery and Data Mining (Vol. 7819, pp. 461-472): Springer Berlin Heidelberg.
